  activeStreamId: null,
  isPlaying: false,
  setActiveStream: (id) => set({ activeStreamId: id }),
  pause: () => set({ isPlaying: false }),
}));
```

### 5. Performance Optimization

- Code splitting (dynamic imports for modals)
- Image optimization (next/image)
- Font optimization (next/font)
